'''梅爾文·里昂·史陶德邁爾一世'''（{{lang-en|Melvin Leon Stottlemyre Sr.}}，{{bd|1941年|11月13日|2019年|1月13日|catIdx=Stottlemyre}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手。11年職業生涯皆效力於紐約洋基。退休後他在大都會、太空人、洋基和紅襪擔任教練長達23年，而他也以教練身分拿下5座世界大賽冠軍。

==職業生涯==
大學時期，史陶德邁爾被洋基球探相中。而他在1961年6月10日與球隊簽約，並從新人聯盟起步。<ref name="sabr">{{cite web|url=https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/b3f6e8d6|title=Mel Stottlemyre|last=Wolf|first=Gregory H.|date=2016|website=Society for American Baseball Research|accessdate=January 15, 2019|archive-date=2020-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200601153738/https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/b3f6e8d6|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1962年，他在小聯盟投出17勝9敗，防禦率2.50的成績。1963年，洋基隊將他升上3A。隔年他更是寫下聯盟最佳的單季防禦率—1.64。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2209&dat=19640922&id=bohjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=B3oNAAAAIBAJ&pg=6123,2037461&hl=en|title=The Right Man|first=Leonard|last=Koppett|date=September 22, 1964|page=8|work=The Telegraph|via=Google News Archive Search|accessdate=June 21, 2015|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409220759/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2209&dat=19640922&id=bohjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=B3oNAAAAIBAJ&pg=6123,2037461&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1964年8月12日，史陶德邁爾登上大聯盟。他在那年拿下9勝3敗，幫助洋基隊連續5年闖進世界大賽。史陶德邁爾在世界大賽強碰紅雀王牌[[鮑勃·吉布森|鮑勃·吉布森]]三次，他在第2場奪勝、第5場無關勝敗，卻在關鍵的第7場吞敗。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1314&dat=19641016&id=9-BXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GekDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4917,252081&hl=en|title=Yankee Gloves, Arms Fail Mel Stottlemyre|last=Missildine|first=Harry|date=October 16, 1964|work=The Spokesman-Review|page=16|via=Google News Archive Search|accessdate=June 21, 2015|archive-date=2016-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513030423/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1314&dat=19641016&id=9-BXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GekDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4917,252081&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1965年，史陶德邁爾入選明星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ALS/ALS196507130.shtml|title=July 13, 1965 All-Star Game Play-By-Play and Box Score – Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103132226/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ALS/ALS196507130.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他拿下20勝，18場完投。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1965-pitching-leaders.shtml|title=1965 American League Pitching Leaders – Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103225232/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1965-pitching-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔年他雖然再次入選明星賽，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NLS/NLS196607120.shtml|title=July 12, 1966 All-Star Game Play-By-Play and Box Score – Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103132240/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NLS/NLS196607120.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過他卻以20敗成為聯盟敗投王。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1966-pitching-leaders.shtml|title=1966 American League Pitching Leaders – Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221034749/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1966-pitching-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>1968年和1969年，史陶德邁爾都拿下單季20勝。<ref name="google.com" />而他更是在1969年擔任明星賽先發投手。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/allstar/1969-allstar-game.shtml|title=1969 All-Star Game Box Score, July 23|work=Baseball-Reference.com|accessdate=January 14, 2019|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119175644/https://www.baseball-reference.com/allstar/1969-allstar-game.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

史陶德邁爾在11年的職棒生涯期間拿下40場完封勝，這個數據和道奇隊的名人堂投手[[山迪·柯法斯|山迪·柯法斯]]一樣多。<ref>{{cite web|title=Career Leaders & Records for Shutouts – Baseball-Reference.com|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/SHO_career.shtml|accessdate=December 27, 2016|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820105425/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/SHO_career.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>1975年球季開打前，洋基隊將史陶德邁爾釋出。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=266&dat=19750327&id=Du4rAAAAIBAJ&sjid=02gFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3106,3227136&hl=en|title=Mel Stottlemyre Released|agency=Associated Press|page=17|date=March 27, 1975|work=Kentucky New Era|via=Google News Archive Search|accessdate=June 21, 2015|archive-date=2016-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518084955/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=266&dat=19750327&id=Du4rAAAAIBAJ&sjid=02gFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3106,3227136&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>爾後他宣布退休，生涯共拿下164勝139敗，防禦率2.97。<ref name="google.com">{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=860&dat=19850201&id=jZlUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=R48DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6596,3156094&hl=en|title=Mel Stottlemyre overcame tragic loss|first=Milton|last=Richman|authorlink=Milton Richman|page=10|date=February 1, 1985|work=Ellensburg Daily Record|via=Google News Archive Search|accessdate=June 21, 2015|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409044456/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=860&dat=19850201&id=jZlUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=R48DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6596,3156094&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

儘管是一位投手，不過史陶德邁爾也有不少精采的打擊表現。1964年9月26日，他單場敲出5支安打。1965年7月20日，他更是敲出場內滿貫全壘打。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/stottme01-bat.shtml|title=Mel Stottlemyre Batting Stats – Baseball-Reference.com|publisher=|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2019-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415220706/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/stottme01-bat.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==紀念==
美國華盛頓州的麥布頓市長，將1964年10月12日這天定為「史陶德邁爾紀念日」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailysunnews.com/news/2014/sep/26/1964-mel-stottlemyre-day-proclaimed-mabton-mayor/|title=1964: Mel Stottlemyre Day proclaimed by Mabton mayor|work=dailysunnews.com|accessdate=June 21, 2015|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627051235/http://www.dailysunnews.com/news/2014/sep/26/1964-mel-stottlemyre-day-proclaimed-mabton-mayor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年，他入選華盛頓州立美國棒球名人堂。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.waalbhof.org/images/hof_2012.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100047/http://www.waalbhof.org/images/hof_2012.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年，洋基隊在主場後方的紀念碑公園放置了一塊史陶德邁爾的匾額。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/yankees-surprise-mel-stottlemyre-monument-park-plaque-article-1.2265454/|title=Yankees surprise Mel Stottlemyre with Monument Park plaque on Old Timers' Day at the Stadium|first=Anthony|last=McCarron|work=New York Daily News|date=June 20, 2015|accessdate=June 20, 2015|archive-date=2019-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531172135/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/yankees-surprise-mel-stottlemyre-monument-park-plaque-article-1.2265454|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Araton|first1=Harvey|title=Yankees Legends, in Various Shades of Gray|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/21/sports/baseball/yankees-legends-in-various-shades-of-gray.html?_r=0|accessdate=June 20, 2015|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=June 20, 2015|archive-date=2019-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190115023553/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/21/sports/baseball/yankees-legends-in-various-shades-of-gray.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==個人生活==
結婚之後，史陶德邁爾和他妻子定居在華盛頓州的[[伊瑟闊|伊瑟闊]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20020915&slug=horn15a|title=Around the horn: Japanese reporter gets vote|first=Larry|last=Stone|work=Seattle Times|date=September 15, 2002|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510121916/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20020915&slug=horn15a|dead-url=no}}</ref>他一共有3個兒子小梅爾、陶德和傑森。除了傑森在11歲因白血病去世外，<ref>{{cite web|last=Donnellon|first=Sam|title="I know he's watching": Courageous brother who died of leukemia molded spirit of Blue Jays' Stottlemyre|url=http://articles.philly.com/1993-10-20/sports/25935972_1_mel-stottlemyre-bone-marrow-transplant-first-father-son|website=[[Philly.com|Philly.com]]|date=October 20, 1993|accessdate=July 6, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063021/http://articles.philly.com/1993-10-20/sports/25935972_1_mel-stottlemyre-bone-marrow-transplant-first-father-son|archive-date=March 4, 2016}}</ref>另外兩位後來也都登上大聯盟。其中陶德更是幫助藍鳥隊在1992年和1993年奪冠的成員之一。

2000年，史陶德邁爾罹患多發性骨髓瘤。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2000/04/10/sports/baseball-yankees-stottlemyre-has-cancer-of-marrow.html|title=Yankees' Stottlemyre Has Cancer Of Marrow|date=April 10, 2000|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2019-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415220512/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/04/10/sports/baseball-yankees-stottlemyre-has-cancer-of-marrow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>後來他在2011年疾病復發。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/harper-mel-stottlemyre-battling-cancer-article-1.2245957|title=Harper: Mel Stottlemyre battling cancer again|publisher=|accessdate=December 24, 2016|archive-date=2019-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416012030/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/harper-mel-stottlemyre-battling-cancer-article-1.2245957|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後他在2019年1月13日去世，享年77歲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/ny-sports-mel-stottlemyre-mets-yankees-obit-20190114-story.html|title=Mel Stottlemyre, New York baseball legend, dead at 77 – NY Daily News|first=Bill|last=Madden|website=nydailynews.com|accessdate=January 15, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116070336/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/ny-sports-mel-stottlemyre-mets-yankees-obit-20190114-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>為了紀念史陶德邁爾，洋基隊整年球季都在球衣衣袖上貼上黑色臂章。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nypost.com/2019/03/28/yankees-are-using-armband-to-honor-mel-stottlemyre/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-08 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107230408/https://nypost.com/2019/03/28/yankees-are-using-armband-to-honor-mel-stottlemyre/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

